name: Framesocket
description: Framesocket is the best way for developers & content owners to tackle video projects of any size. Framesocket is proudly being offered by the team that brought you WellcomeMat, a video system for local publishers, best known as the leader of real estate video. Since 2006, we’ve bootstrapped WellcomeMat, and successfully competed against VC backed and “free” video platforms by squarely focusing on the real estate vertical. We are now profitable and are here to offer the world Framesocket, a powerfully simple video platform for developers and content owners to tackle video projects of any size.
